@base = http://localhost:3000
@planId = 1

### Assign meal to slot
PUT {{base}}/plans/{{planId}}/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-06-29",
  "mealType": "breakfast",
  "mealId": 1
}

### Clear a slot (mealId: null)
PUT {{base}}/plans/{{planId}}/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-06-29",
  "mealType": "breakfast",
  "mealId": null
}
